Develop a complete enterprise-level AI-powered online exam monitoring and cheating detection system called:

“ExamShield AI – Intelligent Smart Proctoring System”

The application must be a real-time cybersecurity-style AI monitoring dashboard built using Python.

TECH STACK:

* Python
* OpenCV
* YOLOv8
* Tkinter GUI
* Pillow
* Pandas
* ReportLab
* Keyboard library
* Winsound
* Haar Cascade
* MediaPipe (optional for iris tracking)

OBJECTIVE:
Create a professional AI exam proctoring system that monitors student behavior during online examinations and detects suspicious activities using computer vision, typing analysis, and behavioral intelligence.

MAIN FEATURES:

1. REAL-TIME FACE DETECTION

* Detect student face using OpenCV Haar Cascade.
* Draw green bounding boxes around faces.
* Display live face count.
* Trigger alerts when multiple faces are detected.

2. MULTIPLE FACE DETECTION
   If more than one face is detected:

* Show “MULTIPLE FACES DETECTED!”
* Trigger warning sound
* Save screenshot evidence
* Add event to dashboard history
* Increase cheating score

3. LOOKING AWAY / HEAD MOVEMENT DETECTION
   Track face position and eye direction:

* Looking left
* Looking right
* Looking center

If student looks away for more than 3 seconds:

* Show cheating alert
* Trigger alarm
* Save evidence screenshot
* Log event
* Increase cheating percentage

4. NO FACE DETECTION
   If no face is visible for more than 3 seconds:

* Display “NO FACE DETECTED”
* Trigger warning alarm
* Save screenshot
* Log suspicious event
* Increase cheating score

5. YOLOv8 OBJECT DETECTION
   Use YOLOv8 model (yolov8n.pt) to detect:

* Mobile phones
* Books
* Laptops
* Additional devices

When detected:

* Draw purple bounding boxes
* Show object label
* Trigger alert
* Save evidence
* Add event to table
* Increase cheating score

6. TYPING SPEED ANALYSIS
   Use keyboard listener to monitor:

* key presses
* typing speed
* abnormal typing patterns

Analyze typing every 5 seconds.

Typing behavior rules:

* <10 keys → Normal Typing
* 10–25 keys → Fast Typing
* > 25 keys → Suspicious Typing

Display:

* typing speed
* typing status
* cheating probability

7. CHEATING SCORE SYSTEM
   Create a live cheating percentage system.

Scoring logic:

* Looking away → +20
* Phone detected → +40
* Multiple faces → +50
* No face → +30
* Suspicious typing → +40

Final score must be limited to 100%.

Display:

* “Cheating Score: 78%”
* real-time updates
* color-coded risk system

Risk Levels:

* 0–20 → SAFE
* 20–50 → SUSPICIOUS
* 50–100 → HIGH RISK

8. PROFESSIONAL GUI DASHBOARD
   Create a modern cybersecurity-style dashboard using Tkinter.

Dashboard must include:

* live webcam feed
* face count
* typing speed
* cheating score
* alert status
* event logs
* dark theme UI
* professional fonts/colors

